# Test with Changes

When you change code in vayeate-theme-studio, add or update tests that cover the change.

## Layer to Test File Mapping

| Layer | Test location |
|-------|----------------|
| State | `src/state/*.test.ts` |
| Actions | `src/actions/*.test.ts` |
| Controllers | `src/controllers/*.test.ts` |
| Data | `src/data/*.test.ts` |
| Viewmodel | `src/viewmodel/*.test.tsx` |
| UI (pages/components) | Colocated `*.test.tsx` next to the component |

## Guidelines

- Prefer testing public behavior and outcomes over implementation details
- Mock `window.electronAPI` in tests that trigger IPC calls (e.g. CREATE_CATALOG)
- Data layer tests use a temp dir; add `@vitest-environment node` when using Node fs APIs
- Before finishing, run `npm run test` in vayeate-theme-studio and fix any failures
